data.description: You'll fall in love with the layout of this beautiful home!  6 min walk to pool via paved sidewalks. Updated cabinets, walk-in pantry and granite countertop kitchen flows into den with fireplace and natural lighting.  Downstairs office with french doors that could be a guest room or 4th bedroom.  Upstairs there is a loft area leading to the 16x16 primary bedroom with attached full bath and large walk in closet. Laundry room with storage and 2 more bedrooms and hall bath upstairs.  Epoxy floored garage with overhead storage, plumbed for 2nd fridge w/ ice maker.  Wooden fence and screened porch in backyard.
